---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import EventCard from "../components/EventCard";
import Streaming from "../components/Streaming.astro";
import ContentCard from "../components/ContentCard.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import loveGod from "../images/pages/love-God.jpg";
import loveOthers from "../images/pages/love-others.jpg";
import impactWorld from "../images/pages/impact-world.jpg";
import RMBM from "../images/pages/RMBM.png";
---

<Layout
  description="Lone Rock Bible Church serves Stevensville and the Bitterroot Valley, Montana. Join us for Sunday worship at 10 AM. Love God, Love Others, Impact the World."
>
  <Hero />

  <!-- Welcome Section -->
  <section class="scroll-reveal max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center px-6 py-16">
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-stone/80 leading-relaxed">
      Lone Rock Bible Church is a non-denominational family of believers located
      in the heart of the beautiful Bitterroot Valley in Montana. We would love
      to have you worship with us. Each week, we gather to worship, pray, and
      study and most of all lift up the name of Jesus in our community.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission sections — alternating layout -->
  <ContentCard
    title="Love God"
    image={loveGod}
    alt="Cross on a scenic mountain with expansive landscape view"
  >
    We love, because He first loved us. We seek to honor God in everything we
    do, from our <a href="/visit">weekly worship service</a> to personal time
    with Him. We firmly believe that God does not call any of us to be spectators
    within the local church — but active and contributing participants. God gives
    each of us strengths and gifts to help encourage and build up the local
    church. All of the ministries within Lone Rock Bible Church are areas where
    you can use your strengths and passions to glorify God through service.
  </ContentCard>

  <ContentCard
    title="Love Others"
    image={loveOthers}
    alt="Group of friends walking together in fellowship and community"
    reverse
  >
    At Lone Rock Bible Church, we believe that the church should be active
    within our local community. Our first priority of service is our local
    community. There are many needs within the Lone Rock and Stevensville
    communities that allow us to show the love of Christ to the community around
    us. Contact the church office to see how Lone Rock Bible Church is currently
    serving our community and how you can get involved.
  </ContentCard>

  <ContentCard
    title="Impact the World"
    image={impactWorld}
    alt="Diverse group of people representing global missions and worldwide ministry impact"
    reverse={false}
  >
    While our first priority of service is our local community — Christ clearly
    tells us and demonstrates that we need to have a passion and vision for
    others around the world. At Lone Rock Bible Church, we strive to offer
    opportunities of service that go beyond our community and even beyond the
    borders of the United States to make an impact for the cause of Christ
    around the world.
  </ContentCard>

  <!-- Events & Streaming grid -->
  <section class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="scroll-reveal">
        <EventCard apiEndpoint="/api/main-calendar" client:visible />
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-reveal stagger-1 space-y-8">
        <Streaming />
        <div class="bg-sand/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-sand">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone mb-4">Vacation Bible School</h2>
          <div class="w-10 h-0.5 bg-accent mb-5"></div>

          <a
            href="https://wwwlonerockbiblechurch.myanswers.com/emerald-crossing/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="block group"
          >
            <img
              src="https://assets.myanswers.com/img/theme/emerald-crossing-logo.png"
              alt="Emerald Crossing VBS"
              class="w-full max-w-xs mx-auto mb-4"
              loading="lazy"
            />

            <div class="border-l-3 border-primary pl-4 py-2">
              <p class="text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-wide">When</p>
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-stone mt-1">
                Mon, July 13 &ndash; Fri, July 17
              </p>
              <p class="text-stone/80 mt-1">5:00 &ndash; 8:00 p.m.</p>
            </div>

            <span class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-primary text-cream text-sm font-medium group-hover:bg-primary-hover transition-colors">
              Register
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Plan Your Visit CTA -->
  <section class="scroll-reveal bg-stone text-cream py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-cream mb-4">
        Plan Your Visit
      </h2>
      <p class="text-cream/70 text-lg mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Whether you're new to the area or looking for a church home, we'd love
        to welcome you this Sunday.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/visit"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 bg-primary text-cream font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-hover transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg"
      >
        What to Expect
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RMBM Banner -->
  <section class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 py-8">
    <a href="https://rmbible.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      <Image
        src={RMBM}
        alt="Rocky Mountain Bible Mission"
        class="mx-auto"
        quality={80}
      />
    </a>
  </section>
</Layout>
